# Files and directories that must NEVER be deployed to Firebase Hosting.
#
# Note: Firebase Hosting itself reads its ignore list from `firebase.json`
# under `hosting.ignore`. This .firebaseignore file is kept as the canonical
# human-readable record of what is excluded — both `firebase.json` and any
# CI / deploy script should respect these patterns.
#
# If you add an entry here, also add it to `hosting.ignore` in firebase.json.

# Developer-only documentation. Contains security rule details, Cloud
# Functions inventory, and internal architecture notes. Must stay private.
dev-docs/
dev-docs/**

